cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and restoration. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves processing of visual media. The use of deep learning models suggests that it may also belong to Machine Learning (cs.LG). Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another possibility as the paper deals with reconstructing images from incomplete data. Finally, Graphics (cs.GR) is a possibility as the paper deals with image restoration.
